00:33:17.470 --> 00:33:18.550 align:middle line:90%
through this whole thing.

00:33:18.550 --> 00:33:19.350 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:33:19.350 --> 00:33:21.190 align:middle line:84%
>> I know that I'm
here for a reason,

00:33:21.190 --> 00:33:23.380 align:middle line:90%
and I'm here for a purpose.

00:33:23.380 --> 00:33:26.050 align:middle line:84%
I've had a few things
that have hurt me

00:33:26.050 --> 00:33:29.590 align:middle line:84%
and knocked me back
