00:33:31.600 --> 00:33:33.910 align:middle line:90%
that everything's hunky-dory.

00:33:33.910 --> 00:33:36.100 align:middle line:90%
And life is plain sailing.

00:33:36.100 --> 00:33:38.200 align:middle line:84%
I've gone through
my frustrations.

00:33:38.200 --> 00:33:40.120 align:middle line:90%
But the only thing that--

00:33:40.120 --> 00:33:42.370 align:middle line:84%
the main thing
that keeps me going

00:33:42.370 --> 00:33:45.160 align:middle line:84%
