go in and resolve everything

00:33:58.570 --> 00:34:00.010 align:middle line:90%
and solve the problems.

00:34:00.010 --> 00:34:01.960 align:middle line:84%
And that would make
me really stressed out

00:34:01.960 --> 00:34:03.730 align:middle line:90%
and tired and drained.

00:34:03.730 --> 00:34:07.240 align:middle line:84%
I used to think that every
problem that happened to me

00:34:07.240 --> 00:34:10.840 align:middle line:84%
or happened on my
path was my problem.

00:34:10.840 --> 00:34:12.400 align:middle line:90%
And I had to fix it.

00:34:12.400 --> 00:34:13.989 align:middle line:90%
I don't anymore.

00:34:13.989 --> 00:34:16.929 align:middle line:84%
I just wait and
observe and then wait

00:34:16.929 --> 00:34:20.650 align:middle line:84%
for the experience,
the lesson to come.

00:34:20.650 --> 00:34:22.300 align:middle line:84%
I don't go and
search for the lesson

00:34:22.300 --> 00:34:25.179 align:middle line:84%
because that's the other thing
that people do to drain--

00:34:25.179 --> 00:34:26.364 align:middle line:90%
>> The reason-- yes.

00:34:26.364 --> 00:34:28.239 align:middle line:84%
>> They kind of go,
what's the reason for it?

00:34:28.239 --> 00:34:29.320 align:middle line:90%
I got to find it.

00:34:29.320 --> 00:34:31.159 align:middle line:84%
And they put pressure
on themselves.

00:34:31.159 --> 00:34:33.520 align:middle line:84%
And if they're not finding
the lesson or the reason,

00:34:33.520 --> 00:34:34.840 align:middle line:90%
they're beating themselves up.

00:34:34.840 --> 00:34:37.510 align:middle line:84%
Because they're like
