00:34:40.510 --> 00:34:42.489 align:middle line:90%
Why am I not getting it?

00:34:42.489 --> 00:34:44.050 align:middle line:90%
I don't do any of that.

00:34:44.050 --> 00:34:48.639 align:middle line:84%
Literally, I am a
passenger to my problems.

00:34:48.639 --> 00:34:50.860 align:middle line:90%
>> That's fantastic.

00:34:50.860 --> 00:34:51.909 align:middle line:90%
>> It sounds weird.

00:34:51.909 --> 00:34:54.000 align:middle line:90%
>> It's great.

00:34:54.000 --> 00:34:55.340 align:middle line:90%
That's got to be a lot easier.

00:34:55.340 --> 00:34:57.880 align:middle line:84%
>> It's a lot easier,
and that's what's change.

00:34:57.880 --> 00:35:00.168 align:middle line:84%
>> So you create at a higher
level because of that.

00:35:00.168 --> 00:35:02.710 align:middle line:84%
Because you don't spend so much
of your energy and resources.

00:35:02.710 --> 00:35:05.400 align:middle line:84%
>> You do create
at a higher level.

00:35:05.400 --> 00:35:09.760 align:middle line:84%
And the thing is people will say
to you when you do it this way,

00:35:09.760 --> 00:35:13.420 align:middle line:84%
they'll say, oh my gosh, I want
the magical powers you have.

00:35:13.420 --> 00:35:15.820 align:middle line:84%
But actually everybody
has the ability.

00:35:15.820 --> 00:35:20.080 align:middle line:84%
It's not something special that
I have and other people don't.

00:35:20.080 --> 00:35:23.360 align:middle line:84%
But so I'll share
with you a funny story

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:28.010 align:middle line:84%
