00:37:31.970 --> 00:37:33.620 align:middle line:90%
Something you never expect.

00:37:33.620 --> 00:37:37.640 align:middle line:84%
It's like another
dimension just opens up.

00:37:37.640 --> 00:37:40.110 align:middle line:90%
And so things started to unfold.

