It's its way of trying
to get your attention.

00:52:46.040 --> 00:52:50.210 align:middle line:84%
>> We'll also to trust the
guidance that you're receiving

00:52:50.210 --> 00:52:52.360 align:middle line:84%
that's in addition
to your senses.

00:52:52.360 --> 00:52:55.960 align:middle line:84%
It's the guidance that's coming
