00:52:59.030 --> 00:52:59.830 align:middle line:90%
guidance.

00:52:59.830 --> 00:53:01.180 align:middle line:90%
We all have it.

00:53:01.180 --> 00:53:04.600 align:middle line:84%
>> Exactly, and it is about
trusting that guidance

00:53:04.600 --> 00:53:08.620 align:middle line:84%
