00:54:20.800 --> 00:54:22.180 align:middle line:90%
>> Gosh, there's quite a few.

00:54:22.180 --> 00:54:28.550 align:middle line:84%
So one of the biggest questions
is, how do I love myself?

00:54:28.550 --> 00:54:31.480 align:middle line:84%
And the response
that I usually give

00:54:31.480 --> 00:54:37.560 align:middle line:84%
people is learn to receive,
stop judging yourself.

00:54:37.560 --> 00:54:42.640 align:middle line:84%
And you have to love yourself
even through your failures.

00:54:42.640 --> 00:54:44.620 align:middle line:84%
Because loving
yourself doesn't mean

00:54:44.620 --> 00:54:46.810 align:middle line:84%
that everything's
going to be amazing

00:54:46.810 --> 00:54:49.780 align:middle line:84%
or to only love yourself
when you're succeeding.

00:54:49.780 --> 00:54:51.850 align:middle line:84%
You have to love
yourself even more when

00:54:51.850 --> 00:54:54.490 align:middle line:90%
you fail because you have to--

00:54:54.490 --> 00:54:58.090 align:middle line:84%
you really have to be
careful about that judgment

00:54:58.090 --> 00:55:00.940 align:middle line:84%
and not judge yourself
when you're failing.

00:55:00.940 --> 00:55:04.570 align:middle line:84%
You have to be your own best
friend through your failures.

00:55:04.570 --> 00:55:06.100 align:middle line:90%
That is really important.

00:55:06.100 --> 00:55:10.330 align:middle line:84%
And you have to get a
little bit at saying no

00:55:10.330 --> 00:55:14.290 align:middle line:84%
and not do things that
you don't want to do

00:55:14.290 --> 00:55:16.390 align:middle line:90%
just because you can't say no.

00:55:16.390 --> 00:55:20.830 align:middle line:84%
So being a six sensory being
is both a gift and a curse--

00:55:20.830 --> 00:55:21.980 align:middle line:90%
