00:56:03.080 --> 00:56:04.990 align:middle line:84%
>> It feels like
it's my calling.

00:56:04.990 --> 00:56:06.570 align:middle line:90%
It feels right.

00:56:06.570 --> 00:56:08.030 align:middle line:84%
I want to leave
the world a better

00:56:08.030 --> 00:56:10.340 align:middle line:90%
