don't judge yourself.

00:56:49.130 --> 00:56:52.230 align:middle line:84%
I want them to know that
what they have is a gift.

00:56:52.230 --> 00:56:53.660 align:middle line:90%
It's not a weakness.

00:56:53.660 --> 00:56:54.920 align:middle line:90%
It's a strength.

00:56:54.920 --> 00:56:59.000 align:middle line:10%
I also want them to know
that not only there's

00:56:59.000 --> 00:57:02.840 align:middle line:10%
nothing wrong with them,
but that the planet needs

00:57:02.840 --> 00:57:05.550 align:middle line:10%
more of them not less of them.

00:57:05.550 --> 00:57:08.030 align:middle line:10%
So don't hide-- you
need to come out.

00:57:08.030 --> 00:57:12.170 align:middle line:84%
If you're sensitive, if
you're empathetic, if only

00:57:12.170 --> 00:57:16.490 align:middle line:84%
