00:57:16.490 --> 00:57:17.540 align:middle line:90%
you need to come out.

00:57:17.540 --> 00:57:19.550 align:middle line:84%
You need to take
leadership roles--

00:57:19.550 --> 00:57:22.220 align:middle line:84%
don't hide, don't
see it as a weakness.

00:57:22.220 --> 00:57:25.400 align:middle line:84%
>> I absolutely
